<section class="appreciation" id="appreciation">
    <div class="content">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>You Are Our Tree Topper</h2>
        <p>Just as Santa places the shining star atop the Christmas tree, you are the highlight that completes our story. Your trust and partnership have been the crowning achievement of our 20-year journey.</p>
        <p>Together, we've created something truly special in the automotive world. Thank you for being our brightest star.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="animation-container">
      <dotlottie-player 
        src="https://lottie.host/070ce607-0ad5-4852-9623-c23c2933e7c9/QRfGgZBrh9.lottie" 
        background="transparent" 
        speed="1" 
        loop 
        autoplay
      ></dotlottie-player>
    </div>
  </section>
    
  <style>
    .appreciation {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
  
    .content {
      background: var(--brand-red);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 4rem;
    }
  
    .text-content {
      max-width: 600px;
    }
  
    .animation-container {
      background: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  
    .animation-container dotlottie-player {
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
    }
  
    h2 {
      color: white;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
  
    p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
  
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .appreciation {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
  
      .content {
        padding: 2rem;
      }
  
      h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
  
      .animation-container dotlottie-player {
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
      }
    }
  </style>